OL,3,CMan, 53, found guilty of rape
OL,4,Ccommitted 23 years ago
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of a rape
OL,7,Fwhich he committed 23 years ago.
OL,9,FSimon Paul De La Haye, 53, maintained
OL,10,Fhe was innocent but was unanimously
OL,11,Fconvicted by a jury at Jersey's Royal
OL,12,FCourt in St Helier on Wednesday 16
OL,13,FOctober - he will be sentenced on 17
OL,14,FDecember.
OL,16,FThe offence took place in November
OL,17,F2002, but an investigation into the
OL,18,Fcrime only started more than two
OL,19,Fdecades later when the victim came
OL,20,Fforward to the police in May 2023.
