OL,6,FOn 20 December 2023, De La Haye was
OL,7,Farrested and interviewed, and
OL,8,Feventually charged on 26 September
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FDetective Sergeant Alasdair Castle
OL,12,Ffrom the Criminal Investigations
OL,13,FDepartment at Jersey Police says: "We
OL,14,Frecognise the immense courage of the
OL,15,Fvictim coming forward to report a
OL,16,Fserious sexual offence after so many
OL,17,Fyears.
